    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"Learn how to summarize the columns available in an R data frame. \\n\",\n",
    "    \"  You will also learn how to chain operations together with the\\n\",\n",
    "    \"  pipe operator, and how to compute grouped summaries using.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
